{"tid":418390,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你地公司多唔多唔憂做既員工？","createTime":"2017-09-29T13:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T12:17:54.000Z","uid":27415,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"198cf096a346dc6f23eeade45b6f9bffb310896c","tid":418390,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"我發覺宜家D私人公司新請番去D staff都係本身唔窮，個個比例係10個入面起碼7個係私樓，有D係一直無停止過請工人姐姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，加上眼見都唔少新既同事仔淨係手袋都貴過佢一個月糧，又可以圍埋一齊討論買珠寶/新手機/去歐遊/買車，每日2杯Starbucks，呢班人都只不過係大學岩畢業 或者係第一份工，可以過呢類生活，真係at least 小康啦<br />\n<br />\n當中個原因會唔會係因為私人公司請人既起薪都唔高，政府人工就一定跑贏大市，結果變左讀得書D窮人後代等錢養家都入曬政府，跟住D有父幹既就係出面D私營公司賺錢買花戴，加上有父幹相對係私營機構都撈得順利D既 無可否認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（以上只係我係中環地區寫字樓所見所聞，其他地方就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ）"},{"pid":"7030157aabe5671912e148e625aba55a9cf5ee5e","tid":418390,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f30cd3ea7226aa6016e66725e75bd6fe116972","tid":418390,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25c5dc45d0cdb721af8b3e272e38127702f78fd","tid":418390,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bec592f7d75737ffd5fb4bdbe38f68f48496f4f","tid":418390,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aece99c73c705dc600507552c36ac8cb93e7c9c","tid":41